## Key Architecture Rules
- Mobile-first (80% mobile traffic)
- Data-driven pages: 1 template + Supabase = 250 suburb pages
- Schema generated from code (`lib/schema.ts`), never plugins
- ISR for static pages with revalidation
- All SEO metadata stored in Supabase, rendered server-side
- No hardcoded content — everything from database
